Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:33.09,SONG-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}FLY! 如心所愿 自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:40.63,SONG-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}就算心灵蒙受创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:47.78,SONG-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}也不要胆怯 因为你早已不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.89,SONG-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}古利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:55.33,SONG-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}无论是谁 都能成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.33,SONG-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}古利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:02.83,SONG-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}舞动吧 朝着那未来的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:10.21,SONG-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}无论何时 电光超人
